## Traps

- `git`, `gh`, `rm`, `uv` are NOT in default PATH for Bash sessions. Use absolute paths: `/usr/bin/git`, `/opt/homebrew/bin/gh`, `/bin/rm`, `/Users/esperie/.local/bin/uv`.
- Pre-commit hook auto-stash conflicts with end-of-file-fixer modifications ‚Äî re-`git add` after the hook fixes a file, then re-commit (per `rules/git.md` ¬ß Pre-Commit Hook Workarounds).
- Branch protection on main rejects direct push for everyone EXCEPT the owner (admin bypass). The "Changes must be made through a pull request" remote message can appear even when push succeeded ‚Äî check the actual `To .../kailash-py.git` confirmation line.
- PyPI cache lag is real (~60s after workflow success). Use until-loop polling on `pypi.org/pypi/<pkg>/<version>/json`, not chained `sleep` (Bash blocks chained sleeps; use Monitor or `run_in_background: true`).
- 5 of the 38 HIGHs are kaizen `tests/unit/judges/` test directory absence (F-D-25) and AutoML token-level backpressure (F-E2-09) ‚Äî both look like quick wins but bear hidden surface area. Read the finding body first.
